because of his stance as ``fierce protector of the wholesome public
image of the Beach Boys ... against the use of hard drugs, namely
cocaine and heroin, by my cousins Dennis, Carl and Brian Wilson.''
   The Love brothers are related to Beach Boys band members Carl
Wilson, Brian Wilson and the late Dennis Wilson.
   A message seeking comment was left with a secretary for Beach
Boys attorney John Branca.
