   _Montana: 6.32; 2.42; 3.32; 0.58; 520.
   _Nebraska: 7.96; 3.73; 2.75; 1.48; 300.
   _Nevada: 7.25; 2.70; 4.04; 0.51; 373.
   _New Hampshire: 3.58; 280; 0.62; 0.16; 193.
   _New Jersey: 31.21; 24.08; 1.95; 5.18; 202.
   _New Mexico: 12.01; 3.90; 6.04; 2.07; 509.
