<HEAD>WASHN: Office Building.</HEAD>
<TEXT>
   The Associated Press and others reported Tuesday that Bush had
settled on Sununu, 49, a blunt-spoken three-term governor, to run
the White House, passing over transition co-chairman Craig L.
Fuller. Fuller has been chief of Bush's vice presidential staff for
