<2ND_LINE>PM-Wall Street 2pm,0298</2ND_LINE>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The stock market showed some scattered gains
today in an advance led by blue chips.
   The Dow Jones average of 30 big-name industrials, which had
