share, up from 85 cents in the comparable period a year earlier.
   Veeco Instruments, which agreed to be acquired by Unitech PLC for
$26.50 a share, jumped 1~ to 24}.
   As measured by Wilshire Associates' index of more than 5,000
actively traded stocks, the market increased $3.60 billion, or 0.14
percent, in value.
   The NYSE's composite index of all its listed common stocks edged
up .28 to 149.24.
   Standard & Poor's industrial index rose 1.09 to 303.93, and S&P's
500-stock composite index was up .78 at 264.60.
   The NASDAQ composite index for the over-the-counter market
